reviewText: Well worth the money if you are a John 5 fan.
Awesome video!  John 5 is not only an amazing guitar player, he is a great teacher and gives a great interview!  I really enjoyed this!
Who plays the guitar like John 5?! Great to see some techniques explained. of his  Anyone that likes Marilyn Manson and Rob Zombie and enjoys playing the guitar will find this "a must have!"
Not much to it, brief interview and a couple of tutorials. He's an excellent guitarist, very versatile and intelligent about managing his career.
